    <Placemark>
      <name>Patiṭṭhāna</name>
      <description><![CDATA[<br>The capital of Aḷaka, the first place to be passed by Bāvarī’s disciples on their way to Sāvatthī (<a href="https://suttacentral.net/snp5.1">Snp.1011</a>). It is identified with the Baithana or Paitana of Ptolemy.]]></description>
